features: Durable Construction: Crafted from good acrylic, our shower rack adhesive replacements are safe, odor-free, and exceptionally durable. They resist rust without the need for drilling and are designed for long-lasting use
Easy installation: Installation is a breeze—no tools needed! Clean the surface first, then just peel and stick. Press the hook onto the wall, and you're all set

Water-Resistant Feature: Designed to thrive in humid environments, these shower adhesive hooks are suitable for bathrooms and kitchens. Their strong adhesive keeps them securely in place without the worry of falling off

Comprehensive Package: This package includes 12 transparent adhesive hooks in three versatile sizes—6x14cm (2.3x5.5 inches), 6x6cm (2.3x2.3 inches), and 7x30cm (2.8x11.8 inches). You'll have plenty to meet all your organization needs

Versatile Usage: Ideal for various applications, these adhesive hooks can be used for corner racks, bathroom storage, kitchen racks, and soap racks. They stick well to tiles, marble, glass, metal, and stainless steel surfaces, helping you keep your home neat and organized
